				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "1) If needed add subclass of LuiComponentAttributes\n\nDecide if a subclass of LuiComponentAttributes needs to be created in order to limit scope issues it everything is implemented in the superclass.\n\nIn this example, a heading level is being added. However its scope is limited to {{gtClass:name=LuiHeading}} . To facilitate this, a new subclass of {{gtClass:name=LuiComponentAttributes}} is created. \n\nSo LuiHeadingAttributes is created and installed in LuiHeading."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
