				"code" : "\tbuilderJob := LcsCompenentAttributeBuilderJob new.\r\tbuilderJob\r\t\tclassPrefix: 'Lui';\r\t\tcreateForRootName: 'ReadOnly';\r\t\t\"attributeName: 'level';\"\r\t\ttagAttributeSetterSelector: #readOnly:; \r\t\tinstallNewClassesInPackageNamed: 'Lcs-WebComponents' tag: 'Attributes';\r\t\t\" componentAttributesClassName: LuiComponentAttributes name; \"\r\t\tcomponentAttributesClassName: 'LuiModelWidgetAttributes';\r\t\tcomponentClassName: LuiModelWidgetAttributes name. \r\tbuilderJob buildJobSteps.\r\t^ builderJob"
